{"tid":1492801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家做好長期戰嘅心理準備未？","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T03:46:22.000Z","uid":65433,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a407849bbed39adf9a279b75b2d9139b7c26e980","tid":1492801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"其實我好擔心運動嘅sustainability<br />\n無錯呢三個月過得好激動人心<br />\n我哋亦都achieve咗好多嘢<br />\n不過我越來越擔心運動無以為繼嘅問題<br />\n老實講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">作為一場抗爭運動<br />\n而家個進度條可能只係去到10%</span></span> (都唔知有無)<br />\n呢個係一個長期嘅抗爭，但係係咪個個都有咁嘅認知呢？<br />\n我日日睇住啲post，覺得有好一部份人都好心急，好似想即刻就贏咁<br />\n唔係話運動唔需要激情<br />\n但個mindset去到now or never咁，只會好快燒盡<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我問大家，多唔多諗過10月1號之後嘅事？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好似大家只係諗住撐到嗰日咁</span></span><br />\n假如到咗十一，除咗嗰日令中共難堪之外，無咩實際成果出到嚟，大家都係要繼續架喎？到時你有無一個正確嘅心態去做一個長遠抗爭嘅準備呢？<br />\n大家問問自己，呢排有無過份聚焦喺啲黑警身上，過份畀憤怒牽住走，而唔係集中喺點樣爭取五大訴求之上？<br />\n屌黑警係應該<br />\n但討論我哋長遠應該點走嘅討論相對嚟講太少啦！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣、統戰、爭取外國支持、輸出革命、特別係好少人討論過嘅資金集中及運用，呢啲全部都係主角</span></span><br />\n至於勇武，我覺得去到呢個POINT，大家都做得好好，但亦要提醒大家心目中都要有一個好清晰嘅picture，勇武喺呢個可能長達十年嘅抗爭之中嘅定位，鼓勵大家目光放遠啲，SET長中期目標。(<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例如建立有系統的training system</span></span>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果我哋唔居安思危，較正心態，將個scale放大返去五年甚至十年<br />\n我哋會好容易畀一時得失蒙蔽</span></span><br />\n就算而家支爆嘅可能性不斷提高，都一定唔係兩三年內嘅事<br />\n<br />\n心態唔正的話，一開學啲人無咁得閒，熱情先無咗一半。去到十一，如果最後係中共嚴陣以待，只能小打小鬧，無突破性發展，熱情再無一半，到時就係運動收皮之日。<br />\n<br />\n所以我真係好希望大家都能夠做好心理準備，較正心態，居安思危！"},{"pid":"2ca11a772a20b0468a34d200c79daf1661084e5f","tid":1492801,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<br />\n一日未完繼續抗爭<br />\n提走美元現金<br />\n減少消費"},{"pid":"4359d1d47131272f2b6d752e539dc488c0aad1e7","tid":1492801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7440656d4df1b1217a48b58aba357e3dd1aba4c8","tid":1492801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fdc65cf2bd5ee44c511ead5f61018628bf40bde2","tid":1492801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2f949ba27b55062d52cb0909b640c976706d64ee","tid":1492801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2e791355cff439d03209e62a5e58783cfabcb31b","tid":1492801,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_ITj0aB7BT4k/TLxUo2cQtYI/AAAAAAAAAQA/vLwPrZV2vzU/s400/landing-sxfl-zhhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F_ITj0aB7BT4k%2FTLxUo2cQtYI%2FAAAAAAAAAQA%2FvLwPrZV2vzU%2Fs400%2Flanding-sxfl-zhhk.jpg&h=3f173601&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41b6b49381359201c2f107a9834d8767fc9240d6","tid":1492801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b58665ec9b283e68af619785a1bdb9dd0f31a152","tid":1492801,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"呢一戰應該係47前最有勝算既一戰。"},{"pid":"253dbf2e4797b99ad66cabb78fa8e8fb80e59005","tid":1492801,"uid":195971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"打從一開始就預左長期戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共用左22年慢慢搞我地,我都預左唔會一時三刻解決到<br />\n所以唔好講邊一方做野係冇用,只需權衡是否有益,一步一腳印終會勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982f04ca021e3e6613c4f902ecbffc298f61e086","tid":1492801,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"報告 準備好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed09de510b4fbe3d3f98c940f78a18769ba9a922","tid":1492801,"uid":292799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:52.000Z","msg":"多啲人去睇"},{"pid":"342db2fe7ea8ed2e7c64887c88ad250dbc03ee63","tid":1492801,"uid":30814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"大家一定要一直保持落去<br />\n如果送中條例通過 義士 有出過黎既人都會送去集中營"},{"pid":"c844d93c43349eac976c13e4e94a664dbfb8f86f","tid":1492801,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c35ce93bdd810167a16969c24be0511e7d185eb","tid":1492801,"uid":260181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"五大訴求一樣都未有<br />\nachieve 到啲乜???"},{"pid":"bedd92240a2e26b8fc4b381c2c3970b31aa85a43","tid":1492801,"uid":275903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"唔好以為嗌口號無用 嗌口號目的唔係班藍絲帶而係班10 後 上次校車班小學雞嗌五大訴求缺一不可是真係好感動"},{"pid":"e7b80f1693772c390f6b8555e9b65bd03b5fc4ae","tid":1492801,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:48:13.000Z","msg":"預左"},{"pid":"6c1b402eb656688c30f7b0896f6d81616cde0d51","tid":1492801,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"22e39e0fa3a9e1617067b040671d323947611a85","tid":1492801,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"之前無人理，今日點都要推多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}